  "section_id": "06-llm-based-automation-is-not-a",
  "title": "LLM-based Automation is not a given",
  "title_translation": "基于 LLM 的自动化并非水到渠成",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "There has been much speculation around the automation of jobs, particularly white collar work, due to AI. An interesting datapoint against this hypothesis can be found in OpenAI’s GDPval paper. OpenAI’s found that human experts were faster and finished tasks for a smaller cost than they would otherwise. With rising capability, humans were augmented, not automated.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0092",
      "parent_block_index": 92,
